text: Justo Albarracín (born 18 May 1951) is an Argentine equestrian. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Argentina Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
